Package view

package view
This package contains the view components for the SC2002 Project. It includes classes that manage the user interface, displaying data and collecting input from users. The view package facilitates interaction between the user and the application by presenting information and capturing user actions.

The classes in this package are responsible for:

  • Displaying menus and prompts to the user
  • Rendering data from the model to the user
  • Capturing valid user input and forwarding it to the controller
  • Providing feedback and messages to the user
